<h2>On-Page SEO for Medical Websites</h2>
<p><a href="/blog/on-page-seo-guide/">On-page SEO</a> is what you control directly on your website. Most healthcare websites fail here because they treat their site like a digital brochure instead of a patient acquisition tool.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Healthcare on-page SEO structure showing service page anatomy" src="/images/blog/healthcare-on-page-seo.webp" /></p>
<h3>Create Dedicated Service Pages</h3>
<p>The biggest mistake healthcare websites make is listing all services on a single page. One "Services" page does not rank for anything specific. You need a dedicated page for every service you offer.</p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Service</th>
<th>Page URL</th>
<th>Target Keyword</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
